reviews.review_text: wow WOW WOW title says it all  this is a great show with a great recording to boot.  Loved the 83 and tours from winter to fall each year. Glad to have been om board during the MUSIC days just the boys and no frills.  music dancing music dancing and alot of travel.  My favorite spanish jam here.  Bar none that i saw.
NICE SHOW! LIL TINNY, BUT GOOD. NICE,SWEET SONGS HERE N THERE. RARE LOCATION.
